      "writtenOn": "2020-12-03T06:09:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Curious: why would the project that `cl` belongs to show up in the AsDepMeta? Isn\u0027t this LUCI project guaranteed to have access to `cl`? Otherwise, CV won\u0027t be able to see this CL at the first place as Gerrit poller won\u0027t return such cl.",
