        "id": 1114919
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-12-03T15:54:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "`cl` belongs to (LUCI) project is a CV construct. Gerrit has no idea about it, and in fact can be misconfigured.\n\nThis is actually common during initial CQ set up or an addition of a new project. Once ACLs are fixed, CV happily snapshot a CL and store it here.",
      "parentUuid": "c6e0d72e_a46e2ae3",
